{"tid":1105194,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登調查] 入嚟放低你嘅phobia","createTime":"2019-04-13T16:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T09:09:44.000Z","uid":160347,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"04971a01424f1b15bd3616fda71a0f3f03e610cc","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:56:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱開電視見到TVB重播法證先鋒大結局，見到個小丑，相信好多人都因為細個套呢套劇所以對小丑有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ai7h8kb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fai7h8kb.png&h=0dedd0aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我自己都有小丑恐懼症(coulrophobia)喺街就算見到正常樣嘅小丑都覺得好恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前無聊上網search過究竟有幾多種phobia, 發覺原來真係乜嘢都可以演變成phobia, 大家都講下你哋嘅phobia吖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a27d4a54173445eab63630ea5856692e3d906d","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:04:36.000Z","msg":"我仲有吞藥恐懼症 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 尤其是係啲又圓又大粒又粉狀嘅藥丸<br />\n每次食藥都有機會卡喺喉嚨到唔上唔落想就想嘔，之後慢慢驚咗吞藥就會一路含住啖水吞唔到，結果粒藥就溶鬼咗變到好苦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時食藥之前同自己講「飲啖水啫」或者「一定吞到嘅！」就真係順利吞咗粒藥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5ac8aea7311015c44795928ddb75fa396d82dd","tid":1105194,"uid":74139,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"深海恐懼症<br />\n會有少少想窒息咁"},{"pid":"f1fb1d5d71a6af0ff6821a6da74137f27501a083","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d5ac8aea7311015c44795928ddb75fa396d82dd","tid":1105194,"uid":74139,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"深海恐懼症<br />\n會有少少想窒息咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"絲打潛過水所以知道?"},{"pid":"d7a9b284164a2b48ec65dd91b798de1a