Time":"2019-04-13T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"Eatalonephobia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:36:24.000Z","msg":"巴打唔講我都唔知原來有呢個phobia <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實我兩三年前都好驚喺街到自己一個人食嘢，因為成日覺得其他人會以為我係冇朋友所以自己食，甚至喺屋企附近自己買外賣返屋企都驚撞到識嘅人<br />\n但我之後慢慢學擺脫人哋一定會以為你係孤獨精嘅諗法，唔洗一定要人陪先可以喺街食飯<br />\n而家叫做好少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63cee6526738065d0727f60e08b0ab734c45780","tid":1105194,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"吞藥我都係咁<br />\n好怕吞葯<br />\n越注意佢就越難吞到<br />\n結果一直唔會吞<br />\n葯會咬爛吞<br />\n膠囊就會拆開嚟食<br />\n成日畀人笑唔識吞葯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過吞到嗰一刻會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f306273ad7c96ff35c72b40a10c884db0f69edd","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a63cee6526738065d0727f60e08b0ab734c45780","tid":1105194,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"吞藥我都係咁<br />\n好怕吞葯<br />\n越注意佢就越難吞到<br />\n結果一直唔會吞<br />\n葯會咬爛吞<br />\n膠囊就會拆開嚟食<br />\n成日畀人笑唔識吞葯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過吞到嗰一刻會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"有同路人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吞完嗰下好有成功感<br />\n藥丸太大粒我會切開半份咁食"},{"pid":"0d02b46961e435426db240b0c2d520cee3f3d5b7","tid":1105194,"uid":121180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4436886e87c68da3462a49372ee8c0bb2b3c23b0","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1bf7897d5f4327d69be567c5f5d4e4245bb4ae1","tid":1105194,"uid":121180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"怕樹 越高大越多葉就越怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦怕蝴蝶 見到啲紋就驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:24:27.000Z","msg":"竟然? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係因為啲樹茂密似某啲嘢定係冇原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢地有生命 又比自己大咁多倍 覺得好恐怖<br />\n海洋公園門口果棵有眼耳口鼻識講野嘅環保樹都好撚驚<br />\n我都唔知自己點解有咁嘅恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲怕大碌果種水渠或者煙囪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好似會俾佢吞噬咁 如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkKPZ4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkKPZ4G.png&h=2291067b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFMF6KQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFMF6KQ.png&h=6e906d23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDMVVDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDMVVDC.png&h=c66e55a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddb27aa6c795bdc5e9991170283b0277416a9bc8","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d02b46961e435426db240b0c2d520cee3f3d5b7","tid":1105194,"uid":121180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4436886e87c68da3462a49372ee8c0bb2b3c23b0","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1bf7897d5f4327d69be567c5f5d4e4245bb4ae1","tid":1105194,"uid":121180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:06:19.000Z","msg":"怕樹 越高大越多葉就越怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n亦怕蝴蝶 見到啲紋就驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:24:27.000Z","msg":"竟然? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係因為啲樹茂密似某啲嘢定係冇原因"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:47:18.000Z","msg":"我覺得佢地有生命 又比自己大咁多倍 覺得好恐怖<br />\n海洋公園門口果棵有眼耳口鼻識講野嘅環保樹都好撚驚<br />\n我都唔知自己點解有咁嘅恐懼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲怕大碌果種水渠或者煙囪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得好似會俾佢吞噬咁 如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GkKPZ4G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGkKPZ4G.png&h=2291067b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LFMF6KQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLFMF6KQ.png&h=6e906d23&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDMVVDC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDMVVDC.png&h=c66e55a2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:00:57.000Z","msg":"有少少明你講被吞噬嘅感覺<br />\n海洋公園隻嘢又係奇怪咗啲嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bb744d207d2dcbc6e19576876c50b7bab4ae2c9","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83ba095168f2416e69a0fef3623a819155f557d0","tid":1105194,"uid":222678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:27:52.000Z","msg":"畏高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:12:10.000Z","msg":"講起畏高我又醒起我多個phobia 係fear of falling (basophobia) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n落啲斜或者岩嶄嘅樓梯就要一級一級咁落<br />\n唔敢上上格床 因為好撚驚會碌落床或者落樓梯次次企喺嗰級勁耐都唔敢落<br />\n去親啲咩昂坪360或者去過Tokyo Skytree觀景台企喺透明玻璃底就驚到仆街 驚下一秒塊玻璃會碎<br />\n但我又唔係畏高喎 係驚跌"},{"pid":"1664b943072c7a95daeb0b995ed3eda279be6c2a","tid":1105194,"uid":194606,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:17:46.000Z","msg":"我有恐音症 Misophonia，尤其是啲人食嘢飲嘢勁撚大聲 Jap Jap Jap，食完之後係咁「吱」口入面嘅嘢，每次一聽到就好唔舒服，同佢講唔該細聲啲，好影響我，佢就話：唔好咁敏感啦，我係咁㗎啦，改唔到喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後唉屌佢老母真係唔撚控制下，我耳仔同個腦成日都受罪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，例如叉刮鐵碟嗰啲高頻率聲音都頂唔順，把聲會喺我腦內徘徊好耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba22f33f3ef1d20bd72f228c74135379580dea53","tid":1105194,"uid":20282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:18:29.000Z","msg":"落樓梯恐懼症<br />\n<br />\n落樓梯個陣會睇到條樓梯係平面而唔係立體<br />\n成日好驚差錯腳跌落去"},{"pid":"6ac492e92ee2e0a0d80d216e1cffc97ae3ef9f34","tid":1105194,"uid":175661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:28:04.000Z","msg":"畏高症"},{"pid":"dc22e1c3ee678a92fc679f73944ceacc45e04e92","tid":1105194,"uid":56151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:29:18.000Z","msg":"Nomophobia"},{"pid":"23167c553df1b8deca2526c2208a0e1074f74d1b","tid":1105194,"uid":222678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a63cee6526738065d0727f60e08b0ab734c45780","tid":1105194,"uid":224561,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"吞藥我都係咁<br />\n好怕吞葯<br />\n越注意佢就越難吞到<br />\n結果一直唔會吞<br />\n葯會咬爛吞<br />\n膠囊就會拆開嚟食<br />\n成日畀人笑唔識吞葯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過吞到嗰一刻會好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:53:09.000Z","msg":"药<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e7a2b998490a452ef37b62481e082dce020852","tid":1105194,"uid":207836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T20:12:25.000Z","msg":"Thantophobia<br />\n死亡恐懼症<br />\n好驚身邊嘅人同動物死"},{"pid":"9a9b8a6f9c77750cd3dbd433ddd6dbfd56c3dc79","tid":1105194,"uid":123677,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T20:26:59.000Z","msg":"interviewphobia"},{"pid":"5a12f2bd88ed29f4672219d47dd2c2818acbf3ee","tid":1105194,"uid":201649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T20:31:17.000Z","msg":"Autophobia 成日都有<br />\n啲人以為我好獨立<br />\n大大下發現自己驚咗依個感覺"},{"pid":"7df85049472d280142c8e44606a216beed96aa89","tid":1105194,"uid":121180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddb27aa6c795bdc5e9991170283b0277416a9bc8","tid":1105194,"uid":160347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d02b46961e435426db240b0c2d520cee3f3d5